## Release Announcement Bitcoin Classic 1.2.5

April 25, 2017.
This release fixes a regression introduced in the 1.2.4 release.

We recommend Bitcoin Classic version1.2.5 for everyone, especially if you already were running a version with thinblocks (xthin).

For more help with installation, and instructions how to download please visit [bitcoinclassic.com/gettingstarted.html](https://bitcoinclassic.com/gettingstarted.html)

